{"tid":360981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"招顯聰在紅磡被捕","createTime":"2017-08-15T17:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T17:31:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e69173c90ad74a47ab358c48deb52fab12085cd","tid":360981,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:31:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1348410-20170815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1348410-20170815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kTTBxhKuG1eO8%2BXVsyK9Qv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e35dee20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1348410-20170815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f135b14d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1348410-20170815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n缺席聆訊被法庭發出拘捕令的招顯聰，下午約5時半在紅磡廣場附近，被巡邏警員發現，將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n律政司不服原訟庭早前就衝擊立法會13名示威者的判刑，向法庭提出覆核刑期，上訴庭改判各人即時監禁8至13個月，招顯聰早上沒有出庭應訊。<br />\n<br />\n案發於2014年，立法會財委會審議新界東北發展前期工程期間，一批示威者衝擊立法會大樓，被裁定非法集結罪成，判處社會服務令，律政司不滿刑期過輕，提出覆核。"}]}